title: I have a vocal range between E3 to A5. What is my vocal type? - Quora

response.answer_text: We can’t tell much without hearing you. How much training have you had - and what style of music are you singing? Anyhow it is a fine and useful range. But asking for vocal type/voice type from this information is a bit like asking: I’m 5’10 - what is my mental character?

If that’s a general range for you, I’m going to assume NOT DIAGNOSE mezzo soprano. I think a voice teacher might have to verify me on that but I also think many other things should come in to play in what makes someone a certain voice type. It’s not just range, it’s also tessitura, tonal quality, and a few other things.
